msgctxt "an8.42:9.1"
msgid "Yāni, bhikkhave, mānusakāni soḷasa vassasatāni, paranimmitavasavattīnaṃ devānaṃ eso eko rattindivo. "
msgstr "Sixteen hundred years in the human realm is one day and night for the Gods Who Control the Creations of Others. "

